e data access request in your Download Manager Installation. <a href=\\"http:\\/\\/www.wpdownloadmanager.com\\/download\\/premium-package-wordpress-digital-store-solution\\/\\" target=\\"_blank\\">Premium Package \\u2013 WordPress Digital Store Solution<\\/a> is required with WPDM for this add-on.\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>API URL:<\\/strong>\\r\\n<pre>http:\\/\\/wp-site-url\\/?wpdm_api=API_KEY&amp;task=API_Call_Fn&amp;parameters....<\\/pre>\\r\\n<strong>Valid API Calls:<\\/strong>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n \\t<li><strong>apiversion<\\/strong>\\u00a0 \\u2014 returns api version<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li><strong>getCategoryList<\\/strong> \\u2014 returns category list<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li><strong>getPackageList<\\/strong> \\u2014 returns package list\\r\\nParams:\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n \\t<li><em>cat_id: specify the category id if\\u00a0 you want to get packages of\\u00a0 a category<\\/em><\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li><strong>getProductList<\\/strong> \\u2014 returns package list with prices when premium package add-on is active<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li><strong>getTodaySales<\\/strong> \\u2014 returns today''s sales when premium package add-on is active<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li><strong>getPackageSales<\\/strong> \\u2014 returns sales of a package when premium package add-on is active\\r\\nParams:\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n \\t<li><em>sdate: start date , format: yyyy-mm-dd\\u00a0 ( optional )\\r\\n<\\/em><\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li><em>edate: end date, format: yyyy-mm-dd ( optional )\\r\\n<\\/em><\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li><em>pid: package id ( required )\\r\\n<\\/em><\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li><strong>getOrderDetails<\\/strong> \\u2014 return details of given order id when premium package add-on is active\\r\\nParams:\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n \\t<li><em><em>oid: order id<\\/em><\\/em><\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li><strong>getOrderByRange<\\/strong> \\u2014 returns list of sales of given date range\\r\\nParams:\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n \\t<li><em>sdate: start date , format: yyyy-mm-dd<\\/em><\\/li>\