(103, 1, '2016-10-10 16:50:36', '2016-10-10 13:20:36', '<img title="Vintage-Logo.png" src="http://localhost/security/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Vintage-Logo.png" alt="Vintage-Logo.png" />\r\n<h2>Our Sweets</h2>\r\nHandcrafted delights that instantly brighten up your day. Whether its chocolate, vanilla or cinnamon, we use the finest ingredients to produce these mouth watering artifacts.\r\n\r\n<figure class="gallery-item"><a href="http://localhost/security/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/foodiesfeed.com_Your-Sunny-Side-Up-2.jpg"><img src="http://localhost/security/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/foodiesfeed.com_Your-Sunny-Side-Up-2-150x150.jpg" alt="foodiesfeed.com_Your-Sunny-Side-Up-2.jpg" width="150" height="150" /></a></figure><figure class="gallery-item"><a href="http://localhost/security/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/foodiesfeed.com_traditional-czech-honey-cake-caffee-latte.jpg"><img src="http://localhost/security/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/foodiesfeed.com_traditional-czech-honey-cake-caffee-latte-150x150.jpg" alt="foodiesfeed.com_traditional-czech-honey-cake-caffee-latte.jpg" width="150" height="150" /></a></figure><figure class="gallery-item"><a href="http://localhost/security/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/foodiesfeed.com_homemade-waffles-with-coffee.jpg"><img src="http://localhost/security/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/foodiesfeed.com_homemade-waffles-with-coffee-150x150.jpg" sizes="(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px" srcset="http://localhost/security/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/foodiesfeed.com_homemade-waffles-with-coffee-150x150.jpg 150w, http://localhost/security/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/foodiesfeed.com_homemade-waffles-with-coffee-300x300.jpg 300w, http://localhost/security/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/foodiesfeed.com_homemade-waffles-with-coffee-768x768.jpg 768w, http://localhost/security/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/foodiesfeed.com_homemade-waffles-with-coffee-1024x1024.jpg 1024w, http://localhost/security/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/foodiesfeed.com_homemade-waffles-with-coffee.